[Student "S"]
{With 11 points in support of \Hs you would generally make a limit raise with this hand. But since partner is in third seat you need to go carefully in case he has opened light. So you bid a Reverse Drury 2\C.

Partner rebids 2\H. What do you say next? 

Partner's 2\H rebid tells you that he opened light. So you pass.}

